Interface KeyValueIterable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    KeyValuePartitionReader, KeyValueStoreReader
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteBufferKeyValuePartitionReader

    @PublicApi
public interface KeyValueIterable
    Interface to be implemented in classes that support iterating over key-value pairs. TODO(cc): Try to get rid of KeyValueIterable and KeyValueIterator when TachyonException becomes a subclass of IOException.
